sequenceDiagram
  actor Caller
  participant API as renderSvgAsync / mountAsync
  participant R as router.classify
  participant M as mermaid (lazy)
  participant N as native reader+renderer
  participant D as diagnostics

  Caller->>API: raw DSL string
  API->>R: classify(dsl) via detectType
  alt flowchart
    R-->>API: tier=native (flowchart, sync path)
    API-->>Caller: themed SVG / interactive (no mermaid loaded)
  else sequence / class / state
    R->>M: loadMermaid() + render to SVG (jsdom in Node)
    M-->>N: mermaid SVG
    N->>N: read model → our layout → themed render
    N-->>Caller: native themed SVG / interactive (drag+reroute)
  else other type (pie, gantt, …)
    R->>M: render fallback SVG
    alt renders cleanly (e.g. pie / browser)
      M-->>Caller: mermaid SVG (themed via themeVariables)
    else degenerate headless (gantt/ER/… under jsdom)
      M->>D: fallback-render-unavailable (error)
      D-->>Caller: clear diagnostic, no broken output
    end
  end
